originalText.text: 3 of my 4 lights have an error code less than 3 years after purchase. Now B and H has discontinued those lights. I have had one fixed under the warranty and now it is having the same error code again and three of my four lights do not work because of this error code. I am not willing to pay almost $200 a light to have them get fixed and for them to have the same error code again. As a photographer bringing my lights on scene I cannot trust this brand of light anymore because I fear they will not work when I need them. Unreliable.
